==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Scragged
<hw>Scrag"ged</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Rough
with irregular points, or a broken surface; scraggy; <as>as, a
<ex>scragged</ex> backbone</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Lean and rough; scraggy.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Scraggedness</ent>⟦br⟧
